postings.body:
Looking for responsible, respectful male to live with two straight, easy going, professionals. Must appreciate view of Midtown skyline from bed and personal outdoor space (this is the best balcony in Astoria).
Details:
 1-br (12` x 12`) of 3-br apartment in 4-yr old building, bath shared with one other roommate;
 $1,700 / month, fully-furnished (queen bed, two dressers, two bookshelves, love seat), including utilities;
 Cable box in-room;
 August 10 - November 10 (flexible within a few days for perfect fit);
 Broadway stop off N/Q trains (ten min to 59th & Lex).
For those interested, please email an introduction, including: age, profession, why you are apartment-searching, and something unique about yourself.
